These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: coral, yellow, red, pink, lavender, light-blue, green
1. the person who likes yellow is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes red##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
4. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes red##1
5. the person who likes green is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Color   | green | pink | lavender | yellow | red | coral | light-blue |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, mystery, spy, crime, epic, adventure, martial-arts
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | epic | spy | adventure | crime | mystery | martial-arts |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
House: wooden, townhouse, gothic-revival, futuristic, craftsman, cottage, art-deco
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is in the middle##1
3. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
5. the wooden house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the cottage house is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| House   | craftsman | wooden | cottage | gothic-revival | art-deco | townhouse | futuristic |

