.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, vegafina, bolivar, cain, old-henry, siglo, bluemaster
1. the siglo-smoker is in the middle##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | bolivar | cain | siglo | alhambra | vegafina | old-henry |

